nodes.name: Given  I open the Ghost login page
And  I enter login email CSV "USERNAME1"
And  I enter login password CSV "PASSWORD1"
And  I am on the posts list page
When  I create a new post with title "My New Post xy" and content "This is the content of my first post"
Then  I should see the post with title "My New Post xy" in the posts list
When  I open the post with title "My New Post xy"
Then  I should not see the post with title "My New Post xy" in the posts list
